==[[Russell Targ]] (again)==

As mentioned before, Targ (on an IP address) and on an account "Torgownik" was editing his article adding in personal commentary and deleting references that were critical of his work in parapsychology. He was told to add reliable references for his claims when editing the article, but he did not listen. He has since complained on his facebook that users with a "hatred" for ESP are editing his Wikipedia article to remove his science career. Of course this is not true, neither is his other claim that Wikipedia banned him from editing his article. This is obviously a case of meat puppetry as he is telling people to come over and edit his article, [https://www.facebook.com/russtarg/posts/848996551792641?fref=nf], his rant has now been spammed around on various conspiracy theory/crank paranormal websites [http://2012thebigpicture.wordpress.com/2014/04/23/whats-your-go-to-research-site-wikipedia-exposed/] [https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10152148242628218&id=295503008217], [http://theeyelessowl.net/2014/04/22/reflections-on-wikipedia-from-russell-targ/] etc. There is now a single purpose account adding in some fringe sources (obviously a friend of Targ), he was reverted but others will probably join in. The issue here though is that users such as myself have found it hard to find any reliable sources for his work in lasers. For example Targ claims to have been a "pioneer" in the earliest development of the laser but it has been hard to find any references for this, I also can't find any sources for his claims about working with NASA, if he did what did he work on? He claims to have worked on airborne laser wind measurements. Any help please appreciated with looking for these sources. [[User:Goblin Face|Goblin Face]] ([[User talk:Goblin Face|talk]]) 19:45, 24 April 2014 (UTC)
: The legion of loons has not yet arrived, if they do, please let me know and I will get the article semi-protected. Your vigilance is appreciated, thank you for keeping an eye on this one. <b>[[User Talk:JzG|Guy]]</b> <small>([[User:JzG/help|Help!]])</small> 21:08, 24 April 2014 (UTC)
