:One problem is the title...[[WP:AT]] tells us to avoid the use of "and" in ways that appear biased.  The current title certainly appears biased, and it encourages people to add Fringe material.  So one of the first things I would suggest is a rethinking of the title.  A re-thinking of the title may also help focus the article on those aspects of the topic that are ''not'' Fringe. [[User:Blueboar|Blueboar]] ([[User talk:Blueboar|talk]]) 17:09, 9 May 2014 (UTC)
