== [[Global Eugenics: Using Medicine to Kill]] ==

Fringe New WOrld Order pushing film. Now at [[Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Global Eugenics: Using Medicine to Kill]], we are getting very inexperienced editors arguing to keep it with arguments such as "Having seen this film, knowing the content and people featured within. and knowing where it gets seen and the following and controversy it has attracted, i'd say it has definite notability." and " The question whether the film is notable enough for Wikipedia could be answered by more research. There's not doubt in my mind that Brooks is notable. The film follows."(while admitting lack of reviews). [[User:Dougweller|Dougweller]] ([[User talk:Dougweller|talk]]) 05:44, 22 June 2014 (UTC)
